berta, whose work is, as a rule, deeply reported, beautifully written,
and perfectly timed. And this new piece is no exception. It features the Tr=
ump campaign=E2=80=99s co-managers, Chris LaCivita and Susie Wiles, boastin=
g about the historic drubbing they believe they have in store for Joe Biden=
, while at the same time =E2=80=9Cprivately praying=E2=80=9D he doesn=E2=80=
