=80=9D he doesn=E2=80=99t make way for a new nominee and thereby compel the=
m to undertake a =E2=80=9Cdramatic reset.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>Before those po=
p-pop-pops caused me to look up at the TV to see what was going on, my plan=
